ncredibles_inside_out-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/pixar">皮克斯</a>确认<i>《超人总动员 3》</i>正在制作中，并宣布推出<i>《头脑特工队》</i>的衍生系列。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="399" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/the-movies-blog/every-pixar-animation-ranked-2539478"><b>每部皮克斯电影按伟大程度排名</b></a></li></ul><p>该动画工作室于周五（8 月 9 日）在迪士尼娱乐展示会上发布了一系列项目公告，并透露已经宣布的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/toy-story-5-confirmed-to-bring-back-woody-buzz-lightyear-3458085"><em>《玩具总动员 5》</em></a>将于 2026 年上映。</p><p> <i>《超人总动员 3》</i>尚未确定确切的上映日期，但据消息称，曾执导前两部电影以及<i>《钢铁巨人》</i>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/the-movies-blog/mission-impossible-ghost-protocol-film-review-781211"><i>《碟中谍 3：幽灵协议》的</i></a>布拉德·伯德也将回归执导《超人总动员 3》的第三部。超级英雄特许经营权。 </p><figure id="attachment_3307667" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3307667" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3307667" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/inside-out-pixar-2015.jpg" alt="由内而外" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/inside-out-pixar-2015.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/inside-out-pixar-2015-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/inside-out-pixar-2015-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/inside-out-pixar-2015-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/inside-out-pixar-2015-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/